ed&yacute;&auml;ndigini, dozasynda &yacute;a-da administratiw
&yacute;ygylygynda &uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meleri&#328; bolandygyny
anykla&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Z&auml;herli b&ouml;wrek zeperlenmesine
&#351;&uuml;bhelen&yacute;&auml;n bolsa, lukman m&uuml;mkin boldugy&ccedil;a
hassany&#328; so&#328;ky sagatlarda n&auml;m&auml;ni alandygyny anyklamaly - bu
bejergini&#328; taktikasyny kesgitlem&auml;ge k&ouml;mek eder.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Conditionagda&yacute;y&#328;
agyrlygyny kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in lukman n&auml;sagdan &yacute;a-da
garynda&#351;laryndan n&auml;sagy&#328; pe&#351;ewi&#328; bozulandygyny,
pe&#351;ew &ccedil;ykaryly&#351;yny&#328; peselmegini &yacute;a-da re&#328;kini&#328;
