<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Synag derini&#328;
re&#328;kine baha bermegi we periferi&yacute;a &ouml;demini&#328; bardygyny,
olary&#328; agyrlyk derejesini barlamagy &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine
al&yacute;ar.&nbsp;B&ouml;wrek &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligini&#328;
k&ouml;pelmegi bilen, bedeni&#328; &auml;hli bo&#351;luklarynda suwuklyk
&yacute;ygnanyp ba&#351;lar, bu &yacute;agda&yacute;da lukman garyn
bo&#351;lugynda palpasi&yacute;a we auskultasi&yacute;a wagtynda lukman ony
kesgitl&auml;r.&nbsp;Bagry&#328; ululygyna hem baha
beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Auskultasi&yacute;a wagtynda d&ouml;&#351;
bo&#351;lugynda hi&#328;lenme &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykar we
&yacute;&uuml;rek sesleri bula&#351;yp biler.&nbsp;Kidneyiti b&ouml;wrek
&#351;ikeslenmesini&#328; ahyrky d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde - uremi&yacute;a - ganda
azotly esaslar bar, patogenomiki alamat &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar -
&yacute;&uuml;regi&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi wagtynda perikardy&#328;
s&uuml;rt&uuml;lme sesi.&nbsp;N&auml;sagda adaty bolmadyk &yacute;&uuml;rek
ritmi bolup biler.&nbsp;B&ouml;wrek &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi bilen
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; hereketi bozul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Lukman hassadan hajathana n&auml;&ccedil;e gezek
bar&yacute;andygyny, tabury&#328; tebigatyny soramaly.</span></p>

